## A “decision tree” you can use tomorrow

```{mermaid}
flowchart TD
  A[Do you have predicted outcomes Ŷ being used as Y?] -->|No| Z[Standard inference]
  A -->|Yes| B[Do you have any labeled Y?]
  B -->|No| C[You can do prediction + descriptive summaries,<br/>but inference needs assumptions or new labels]
  B -->|Yes| D[Is labeled set representative of target use?]
  D -->|No| E[Use design/sensitivity adjustments;<br/>report limits of transportability]
  D -->|Yes| F[Use IPD methods (e.g., ipd);<br/>report calibration + uncertainty]
```

